Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini adalah festival olahraga gabungan\Ntahunan atau Hari Olahraga SMA Kalmia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tempat Arthur dan Marie bersekolah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta sekolah saudarinya, SMA Perennial.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, karena kedua sekolah\Nakan segera bersatu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka memutuskan mempertahankan nama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari sekolah pemenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu terlalu dipaksakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tempat ayahku bersekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta tempatku bersama Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau mempertahankan nama Kalmia,\Napa pun yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari bekerja sama\Nuntuk melindunginya, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Nona Marie,\Npelayan keluarga Zetes, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Daryl Blofeld, murid di SMA Perennial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Tuan Daryl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat populer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sahabat\NTuan Arthur yang jutek itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku punya permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kamu bisa memberitahuku acara\Napa yang akan diikuti Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski sekarang kita lawan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku masih mau melihat sahabatku,\NArthur, beraksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya tak pernah mendengarnya bilang\Npunya sahabat sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur sebenarnya tak suka paprika hijau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur ikut Kompetisi Berkuda\Ndan Pertarungan Kavaleri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.\NKamu banyak membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mendorong dua sekaligus itu berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu dari Klub Penggemar Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau menyelesaikan ini\Nsebelum Kompetisi Berkuda Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti perasaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terlambat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada telinga kuda di kepala kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita memakai ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur mungkin mengira kami kuda,\Nlalu menunggangi kami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu...\N- Waktunya mulai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tuan Carl dan Nyonya Charlotte.\N- Kompetisi Berkuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pasti bisa, Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah yang disebut menyatu dengan kuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rintangan berikutnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga menyelesaikannya dengan mudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali jatuh di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya berjalan lancar sampai tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh jika dia tiba-tiba\Nkehilangan kendali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bip-bip, bip-bip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengintai Tempur: Bahaya terdeteksi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maaf membuat kalian khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika gelisah,\Nkalian akan menakuti kudanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa tolong periksa dahulu\Napakah kudanya terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, kamu juga harus ke UKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku akan segera ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda baik-baik saja, Tuan Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, lihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peluru pistol angin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang menembak kuda di antara matanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini perbuatan pembunuh itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini terlalu kekanak-kanakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat Anda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kamu tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda tak perlu menahan diri.\NKatakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Naku hanya akan mengatakan ini padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertemu Daryl saat kami SD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebelum aku ditunjuk sebagai pewaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya kamu dapat nilai sempurna lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hanya anak simpanan,\Ntapi sangat arogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kamu merobek mulutku,\Naku tak akan mengaku dirundung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku tak mau mengecewakan ayahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, kita akan mengadakan\Nkompetisi sketsa sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan berpasangan menjadi satu kelompok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu mau berpasangan denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua sampah dalam satu tim.\NCocok sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl adalah anak di luar nikah sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah memintaku\Nmenjadi rekanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi hanya ini yang kumiliki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Mereka juga membuang punyamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, hanya ini yang tersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, untuk warna yang hilang, kita bisa\Nsaling memakai atau mencampur catnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita\Nmembuat warna baru bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berdua?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kita bisa melakukannya\Njika bekerja sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, kamu tak sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, apa pun yang kulakukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl akan bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ulang tahunmu tanggal 4 April?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulang tahunku juga sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat bersamanya,\Naku selalu merasa bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?\NPartiturnya hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu sudah menghafalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, tanpa partiturnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minumlah ini\Ndan tenangkan dirimu dulu, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan di hari debut sosialku,\NDaryl ada di sisiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, tiba-tiba aku merasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, kamu berlatih tanpa henti\Ntanpa tidur atau istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti karena itu\Nkamu terlalu memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yang paling tahu\Nbetapa keras kamu bekerja
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena kita teman baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak lama setelah itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl, entah apa dia\Nakan menyukai hadiah ulang tahun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini untuk bulan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, itu sangat memuaskan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatnya tertidur\Ndi hari debut sosialnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Obat tidurmu sangat membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluargaku mengelola rumah sakit.\NItu bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ini partitur musiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan aku belum memulai debut sosialku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nilainya selalu lebih tinggi dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat wajahnya saja membuatku marah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, dia menganggapku\Nsebagai sahabatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucu sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali, tembak kami dengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pistol angin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Luar biasa!\N- Pastikan kamu tak mengenaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Daryl sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya mengerti.\NSaya akan ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:11:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan Tuan Arthur\Ntak sepenuhnya membenci Daryl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah meski bohong,\Nitu kenangan indah baginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus membuat Daryl menghentikan\Nkejahatannya terhadap Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar Arthur cedera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sepertinya pergelangan kakinya terkilir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peserta di ajang terakhir,\NPertarungan Kavaleri, silakan bersiap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peserta di ajang terakhir,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pertarungan Kavaleri, silakan bersiap.\N- Awalnya, pertandingan terakhir ini
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seharusnya antara Arthur dan Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena cedera,\Ndia mungkin tak bisa bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur tak bisa ikut\Ndalam Pertempuran Kavaleri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kita mau menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peserta Balap Karung Kentang,\Nsilakan berkumpul di depan gimnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Tuan Arthur tak bisa berpartisipasi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari tebus itu\Ndengan Lomba Karung Kentang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pandai dalam hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar ada lomba estafet\Ndan lomba individu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita bisa bersaing\Ndi tim yang sama, Marie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak butuh bantuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya alasan sendiri untuk bersaing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka orang mencurigakan\Ndi lokasi festival olahraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami berpencar dan mencari
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di seluruh tempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu bilang akan mencincang Noah\Njika melihatnya lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka semua murid dari SMA Perennial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMA Perennial...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira mereka bekerja\Ndi bidang yang sama denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menduga\Nmereka akan memakainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pistol angin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebesar apa pun mereka mau\Nmempertahankan nama sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini sudah keterlaluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl adalah dalangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sahabat" adalah\Nteman yang sangat dekat dan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bukan sahabatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl hanya ingin\Nmerebut semuanya dari Tuan Arthur
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mendorongnya ke jurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melindungi Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jika tak punya tim,\Nkamu tak akan bisa bersaing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan mempertaruhkan nama sekolah,\Nskornya sangat ketat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang kita sudah mencapai\Nacara terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tawa atau air mata,\Npertandingan ini akan menentukan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan Pertarungan Kavaleri adalah\Ntim kalah jika penunggangnya jatuh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau jika ikat kepala mereka\Ndiambil oleh lawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuda lawan sepertinya cukup kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, Nona Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur pasti cedera,\Njadi, dia tak bisa bersaing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, bukankah itu juniormu dan Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, dia pernah membantuku menangkap ayam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku minta dua orang\Nuntuk menolongnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya Arthur tak bisa berpartisipasi\Nkarena cedera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menantikan pertarungan sahabat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi Tuan Arthur,\Naku tak boleh kalah darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari bertarung dengan adil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertandingan akan segera dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah, kita akan memenggal kepala Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu pertandingan dimulai,\NSMA Perennial menyerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan menang untuk Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku membalas budi yang tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggota Klub Penggemar Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMA Kalmia unggul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para gadis cantik\Nmemamerkan keahlian mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka tersandung?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dua tim jatuh!\N- Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, sesuatu mengenai kakiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah itu pistol angin lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, jangan berpaling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saatnya beraksi serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedua sekolah bertarung dengan sengit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bergerak\Nsampai rasa sakitnya mereda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senior Toby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah berjuang keras\Nuntuk mempertahankan nama sekolah kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, kamu belum dengar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie bertarung menggantikanmu,\Nmelawan sahabatmu, Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam sekejap mata, skornya menjadi 2-1\Ndengan Perennial memimpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula,\Nkuda-kuda yang ditunggangi Daryl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah pemain kuat yang memimpin\Ntim rugbi ke Kejuaraan Nasional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertandingan ini akan menarik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, mustahil kamu bisa mengalahkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang satu lawan satu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisi mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Astaga!\N- Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, Kuda dari SMA Kalmia\Ndalam keadaan berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Bukankah itu pelanggaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jatuh dari kuda berarti kamu keluar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi karena dia belum mendarat,\Nitu masih legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kamu di sini hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan jarak dekat\Nyang melanggar peraturan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa kamu menemukan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetap saja,\Naku bisa merasakan kemarahanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Arthur masih menganggapku\Nsebagai sahabatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, itu yang dia yakini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat apanya?\NDasar pembohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena orang sepertimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur tak bisa memercayai orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mempermainkan perasaan orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan memaafkan\Nsiapa pun yang menyakiti Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuda-kuda SMA Perennial akhirnya tumbang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemenangnya adalah SMA Kalmia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak bisa memercayai siapa pun lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang yang tak bisa\Nmenjaga hubungan normal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak bisa menjadi pewaris yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang\Ntak punya saingan yang kuat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur memukul seseorang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bersahabat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl Blofeld curang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya buktinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl mengancam akan membuat kami\Ndikeluarkan jika tak membantunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu apa yang dia bicarakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan aku tak melawan\Ndan berpura-pura lemah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah untuk mendapatkan bukti kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak yang hanya bisa menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita teman baik, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi orang sepertiku, yang tak punya\Ntempat di rumah atau di sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keberadaanmu adalah penyelamatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai aku bisa kembali ke masa-masa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku tak membutuhkannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa ada bagian yang rusak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Maafkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya melakukan ini tanpa izin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, saya selalu percaya\NAnda bisa melakukannya, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahwa Anda bisa mengatasinya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Anda orang yang sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak benar, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya kuat karena kamu bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih karena selalu memihakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, aku tak bisa melihat ini.\NAku sangat sibuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah membantuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kamu tak perlu berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami melakukan ini karena ingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah sudah berapa tahun sejak terakhir\Naku mendengar Tuan Muda bermain piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iramanya energik dan elastis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kamu memainkan instrumen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}musiknya jelas mencerminkan\Nkondisi pikiran pemainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya, semua hidup dengan damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Liburan ke Pulau Selatan\Nbersama Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Tuan Roy, Marie-2,\NTuan Carl, Nyonya Charlotte, Nona Isabel,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah, dan Prototype 26 muncul,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu...
